Source: CONTRIBUTING.md

How to Contribute

  • Vignettes can be acessed at https://mjanuario.github.io/evolved/, or by downloading the package from CRAN or github (see instructions in the website).
  • If you want to contribute with functions or tutorials, please reach out to Matheus Januario (januarioml.eco [at] gmail.com), and we can work with you to add new material and data to the site
  • Alternatively, your contributions or new lessons are welcome as Pull Requests.

Reporting Issues or Problems using github

  • To report issues, bugs, or problems with either the material, the functions, or the wbesite please open an issue on our github page and we will be happy to address it.
  • Alternatively, send an email to Matheus Januario (januarioml.eco [at] gmail.com).

Support

  • Send an email to Matheus Januario (januarioml.eco [at] gmail.com).
  • Open an issue if there’s anything we can do to help!
